## § DATABASE RULES

Drizzle ORM is the ONLY ORM. Prisma is FORBIDDEN.

| Correct | Forbidden |
| --- | --- |
| `import { db } from '@/lib/db'` (Drizzle) | `import { prisma } from '@/lib/prisma'` |
| `drizzle-kit generate` | `prisma generate` |
| `drizzle-kit migrate` | `prisma migrate` |
| `drizzle-kit studio` | `prisma studio` |
| `@neondatabase/serverless` | `@prisma/client` |

If Prisma files are found (`schema.prisma`, `prisma/`): plan migration to Drizzle in dedicated phase.

