## § EMAIL RULES

React Email + Resend is the ONLY email stack. `nodemailer` is FORBIDDEN.

| Correct | Forbidden |
| --- | --- |
| `import { Resend } from 'resend'` | `import nodemailer from 'nodemailer'` |
| `import { Body, Html } from '@react-email/components'` | Raw HTML string templates |
| `resend.emails.send({ react: <Template /> })` | `transporter.sendMail()` |

Email templates live in `lib/email/templates/`. Dev preview: `pnpm email:dev`.

