## § SECURITY RULES

Arcjet is the unified security layer. Nosecone handles CSP/Headers.

| Concern | Tool | NOT |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Rate limiting | Arcjet `tokenBucket` | `@upstash/ratelimit` |
| Bot protection | Arcjet `detectBot` + `shield` | Custom middleware |
| CSP / Headers | `@nosecone/next` in `proxy.ts` | Manual headers |
| DDOS mitigation | Arcjet `shield` | Nothing |
| Cache/Queue | Upstash Redis | — |

Upstash Redis is KEPT for cache, queue, and session storage. NOT for rate limiting.

