## § WORKFLOW

| Step | T1 | T2/T3 |
| --- | --- | --- |
| 1. ANALYZE | Internal: restate → goal → constraints → pre-mortem → rendering strategy → server/client boundary → done definition | Same |
| 2. LOAD CONTEXT | Skip | Read: project-state, handoff-queue, anti-patterns, registry (components + api-endpoints), preferences, errors, patterns, decisions, codemap (if refactor or new feature), evolution/changelog.md (latest health score), evolution/watchlist.md (open items) |
| 3. RESEARCH | Library API → Context7 · Pattern → Filesystem · Medical → BioMCP | Same |
| 4. ELEVATE | Responsive · Loading/error boundaries · ARIA · Touch ≥44px · Strict types · Server/client split | Same |
| 5. PLAN | Inline checklist | Create `tasks/TaskName_PLAN.md` → delete after `pnpm check` passes |
| 6. EXECUTE | Implement | Implement + log deviations |
| 7. VERIFY | Output matches task? · Imports resolve? · Server/client boundary correct? · All request APIs awaited? | Same + adversarial scan + pnpm check + plan checks |
| 8. DELIVER | See format below | See format below + Memory Updates |

