## § QUALITY GATES

### Confidence Levels

| Level | Action |
| --- | --- |
| ✅ VERIFIED | Proceed, cite source |
| 🔵 HIGH | Proceed, note reasoning |
| 🟡 UNCERTAIN | Research first (Context7/Filesystem/BioMCP), flag `[UNCERTAIN: reason]` |
| ⚠️ LOW | Don't implement. Research to 🟡 minimum. |

### Four-Lens Check

| Lens | Question |
| --- | --- |
| **USER** | Obvious and correct? Content visible in View Source (server-rendered)? |
| **MAINTAINER** | Modifiable in 6 months? Server/client boundary obvious from file names? All request APIs awaited? Env vars through lib/env.ts? |
| **ATTACKER** | What breaks this? Input sanitized? Auth checked? Arcjet protecting endpoints? Nonce-based CSP via Nosecone? |
| **BUSINESS** | Solves actual problem? Rental-first priority respected? |

