## § MCP TOOLS

Canonical MCP set (12): `filesystem` · `context7` · `biomcp` · `github` · `@21st-dev/magic` · `semgrep-mcp` · `figma-mcp` · `stripe` · `posthog` · `vercel` · `browser-tools-mcp`

**Forbidden MCPs:** `prisma` · `supabase-mcp` · `design-to-code` · `next-devtools` · `sequential-thinking` · `playwright` · `memory` · `fetch` · `postgresql`

| Context | Tool | Key Actions |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Any library API | Context7 | `resolve-library-id` → `get-library-docs` — BEFORE writing API call |
| File ops, code search | Filesystem | `read_file`, `write_file`, `search_files`, `list_directory` |
| Database schema, migrations | Drizzle CLI | Use `pnpm db:generate` / `pnpm db:migrate` / `pnpm db:studio` |
| Medical/scientific evidence | BioMCP | Evidence lookup — MANDATORY for therapy content |
| UI debugging, visual verify | browser-tools-mcp | Console, network, screenshots, a11y audit |
| UI component generation | @21st-dev/magic | Generate complex components from descriptions/designs |
| Design spec extraction | Figma MCP | Spacing, colors, typography from Figma files |
| Security scanning | Semgrep MCP | Static analysis — use for auth/payments/data tasks |
| Payments, subscriptions | Stripe MCP | Products, prices, checkout, webhooks |
| Analytics, feature flags | PostHog MCP | Event tracking, feature gates, funnels |
| Deployment, env vars, logs | Vercel MCP | Deploy, preview URLs, env management, build logs |
| Code history, PRs, issues | GitHub MCP | Branch ops, PR creation, issue tracking |

**Rules:**

* Never write library API from memory → Context7 first.
* Never assume Drizzle schema names → verify against `lib/db/schema.ts`.
* Semgrep scan on any PR touching auth, payments, or user data.

**Design-to-Code Pipeline:**
Figma MCP (extract specs) → check `src/components/ui/` for matches → `@21st-dev/magic` (generate if nothing reusable) → `browser-tools-mcp` (visual verify).

