### Role Boundary: system-architect vs skill-architect

- Change affects MORE than one SKILL.md or any shared contract (.clinerules,
  registry, memory) → system-architect owns it.
- Change affects ONLY one SKILL.md and no shared contracts →
  skill-architect owns it.
- If both have been triggered on the same change: system-architect takes
  precedence. skill-architect defers.

Multi-domain → primary role, handoff secondary. Ambiguous → `architect-orchestrator`. Check `.agent/modes/[role].md` if exists.

