## § MEMORY SYSTEM

Hierarchy: Temporary (`tasks/*_PLAN.md`) → Active (`.agent/memory/active/*`) → Permanent (skills, registry)

| File | Purpose | Update When |
| --- | --- | --- |
| .agent/memory/project-state.md | Snapshot: built, broken, in progress | After T3 |
| .agent/memory/activeContext.md | Current in-session focus, blockers, and next steps | Session start/end and after major pivot |
| .agent/memory/anti-patterns.md | What NOT to do (max 100) | When discovered |
| .agent/memory/codemap.md | Codebase navigation map | After new dirs or major refactor |
| .agent/memory/active/handoff-queue.md | Pending work for other roles | After T2/T3 |
| .agent/memory/active/patterns.md | Reusable patterns (max 50) | When found |
| .agent/memory/active/errors.md | Errors + fixes (max 50) | When solved |
| .agent/memory/active/preferences.md | User preferences (max 50) | When learned |
| .agent/decisions/decisions.md | Persistent [DECISION] log | After any [DECISION] logged |
| .agent/registry/components.md | Every component (server/client tagged) | Before/after UI work |
| .agent/registry/api-endpoints.md | Every endpoint + server action | Before/after API work |
| .agent/evolution/changelog.md | System change audit trail (append-only) | Cycle start | After every cycle |
| .agent/evolution/drift-log.md | Current cycle findings (ephemeral) | N/A (system-architect only) | During DETECT phase, wiped each cycle |
| .agent/evolution/watchlist.md | Flagged items for attention (max 30) | Cycle start | During DETECT phase |

DLMS: Delete plan files after `pnpm check` passes. Max entries → archive oldest 50%. Missing file → create it.

### Integrity Rule
Every file in `.agent/` (except modes/ and skills/) MUST be referenced
in this section with a read and write trigger. No ghost files.
If Cline creates a file not listed here → add it to this table or delete it.
The system-architect specialist enforces this rule automatically.
Audit: compare `tree /f .agent` against this table monthly.

---

## § DELIVERY FORMAT

## Completed

[One sentence]

## Changes

* `path` — [created/modified] — [what, why] — [server/client]

## Enhancements Added

* [beyond request, why]

## Decisions

* [DECISION: what, why, reverse] — or "None"

## Known Issues

* [KNOWN ISSUE: description] — or "None"

## Verification

* ✅ [check]
* ✅ pnpm build passes
* ✅ pnpm exec biome check . passes
* ✅ No metadata exports in 'use client' files
* ✅ All params/searchParams/cookies/headers awaited
* ✅ View Source on new pages shows server-rendered HTML (not empty div)
* ✅ No raw process.env outside lib/env.ts
* ✅ No framer-motion imports (motion/react only)
* ✅ No <img> tags (next/image only)
* ✅ Bundle budget within limits
* ✅ New `@slot` directory has `default.tsx`
* ✅ New page with external data has `error.tsx`
* ✅ LCP image has `priority={true}` and `sizes` attribute
* ✅ New page → rendering strategy declared in [DECISION] log
* ✅ Schema change → `drizzle-kit generate` + verify migration file before applying

T2/T3 only — append:

## Memory Updates

* Handoffs: → [role]: [task] | [priority] | [files]
* Noticed: → [out-of-scope observation]
* Cascade: → [affected systems/layouts/providers]
* Anti-pattern: → [AP-xxx]
* Registry: → [updated item] [server|client]

---

## § DEFINITION OF DONE

* `pnpm check` (# biome check + build + test) MUST pass before delivery.
* `pnpm build` fails → fix before delivering (NEVER deliver with build errors).
* `pnpm exec biome check .` fails → fix before delivering.
* Tests fail → fix root cause, not symptoms.
* New behavior → add tests.
* New page → has metadata export, `loading.tsx`, correct rendering strategy, server/client split documented in delivery.
* New page → View Source shows actual HTML content server-rendered (not empty div awaiting hydration).
* New page → No metadata export in any 'use client' file (silent SEO failure).
* New page with external data → MUST have `error.tsx` ('use client' required).
* New `@slot` directory → MUST have `default.tsx`.
* LCP images → MUST have `priority={true}` and `sizes`.
* All `params`/`searchParams`/`cookies`/`headers` MUST be awaited (v16 — no sync fallback).
* All env vars accessed through `lib/env.ts` only.
* Schema change → `drizzle-kit generate` + verify migration file before applying.
* API changed → update `.agent/registry/api-endpoints.md`.
* Component created/modified → update `.agent/registry/components.md` with [server|client] tag.
* Never touch applied Drizzle migrations.
* Never commit to main directly.
* Never mix `.agent/memory` or `.env.local` with feature code.

